Flask-BS4 Changelog
===================


Version 4.4.1.6
---------------

Released on February 25th 2020

-   Update: Sample app cleanup
-   Update: `setup.py` no longer lists support for v2
-   Update: Remove components
-   Update: Components `modal` renamed to `modals`
-   Add: `render_field` filter
-   Update: `render_form` uses `render_kw` with `xmlattr`
-   Update: `render_form` uses `render_kw`
-   Add: `cards` component
-   Fix: `quick_form` attributes cleanup
-   Fix: `render_form` uses `render_kw` as v3
-   Fix: `render_form` uses the manual `enctype`
-   Add: form can have `novalidate` attribute
-   Add: component `modal` with automatic button
-   Fix: Button `**kwargs` are used in component
-   Fix: button `type` maps to `design` for historic
-   Fix: `btn` components apply size
-   `quick_form` uses internally `render_form`
-   Set theme jekyll-theme-minimal


Version 4.4.1.5
---------------

Released on February 25th 2020

-   Add: Makefile
-   Add Validation to `render_form` (#1)
-   Add: Components.Modal with focus and button
-   Fix: `enctype` has no index if no `FileField`
-   Add: Components.Buttons in different variations
-   Modify sample app for `forms.render_form`
-   Fix: `forms.render_form` creates correct fields
-   Update .gitignore to ignore .vscode
-   Feature: Add Sample App to view the Input Fields


Version 4.4.1.4
---------------

Released on January 10th 2020

-   Fix: Use bootstrap/static for html5shiv & respond
-   Cleanup template formatting of Jinja fields
-   Update make-release to add new version to CHANGES


Version 4.4.1.3
---------------

Released on January 10th 2020

-   Delete `base.html.j2` template to use the standard
-   Add `html5shiv`
-   Add `respond.js`


Version 4.4.1.2
---------------

Released on January 7th 2020

-   Fix: Add dependency to `Flask-WTF>=0.14.0` in `setup.py`
-   Fix: Rendering of `BooleanField` allgnment


Version 4.4.1.1
---------------

Released on January 6th 2020

-   Update to Bootstrap 4.4.1
-   Update to jQuery 3.4.1
-   Update to Popper 1.16.0


